            <title><![CDATA[【[话筒]#光靠迈开腿减不了肥#】你在减肥路上走过哪些弯路吗？医生提醒，#减肥要避免3个误区#：①光靠运动就能减肥。除了“迈开腿”，还要“管住嘴”；②吃素食...]]></title>
            <description><![CDATA[【<span class="url-icon"><img alt="[话筒]" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/m/emoticon/icon/others/o_huatong-0a3e80b147.png" style="width:1em; height:1em;" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%85%89%E9%9D%A0%E8%BF%88%E5%BC%80%E8%85%BF%E5%87%8F%E4%B8%8D%E4%BA%86%E8%82%A5%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%85%89%E9%9D%A0%E8%BF%88%E5%BC%80%E8%85%BF%E5%87%8F%E4%B8%8D%E4%BA%86%E8%82%A5%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#光靠迈开腿减不了肥#</span></a>】你在减肥路上走过哪些弯路吗？医生提醒，<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%87%8F%E8%82%A5%E8%A6%81%E9%81%BF%E5%85%8D3%E4%B8%AA%E8%AF%AF%E5%8C%BA%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%87%8F%E8%82%A5%E8%A6%81%E9%81%BF%E5%85%8D3%E4%B8%AA%E8%AF%AF%E5%8C%BA%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#减肥要避免3个误区#</span></a>：①光靠运动就能减肥。除了“迈开腿”，还要“管住嘴”；②吃素食或不吃主食。虽然能短时间内掉秤，但难以持久，也会带来副作用；<br>③滥用减肥药。滥用药带来的风险远远超过受益。👇🏻<a href="https://m.weibo.cn/search?containerid=231522type%3D1%26t%3D10%26q%3D%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23&amp;extparam=%23%E5%B0%8F%E5%8D%AB%E5%94%A0%E5%81%A5%E5%BA%B7%23" data-hide=""><span class="surl-text">#小卫唠健康#</span></a>（央视新闻）<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034:5011188891713616" data-hide=""><span class="url-icon"><img style="width: 1rem;height: 1rem" src="https://h5.sinaimg.cn/upload/2015/09/25/3/timeline_card_small_video_default.png" referrerpolicy="no-referrer"></span><span class="surl-text">央视新闻的微博视频</span></a><br clear="both"><div style="clear: both"></div><video controls="controls" poster="https://tvax2.sinaimg.cn/orj480/002TLsr9ly1hnog7m0rjlj61ri0zqb2902.jpg" style="width: 100%"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/XN8AxcEFlx08derZAZAQ01041201Lyc30E010.mp4?label=mp4_720p&amp;template=1280x720.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1710537294&amp;ssig=S7FqvcRRw2&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/vOaRtsbElx08derZ9LUs01041200XNvP0E010.mp4?label=mp4_hd&amp;template=852x480.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1710537294&amp;ssig=BjfX%2F2ckAl&amp;KID=unistore,video"><source src="https://f.video.weibocdn.com/o0/xnFNtJ26lx08derZ7Au401041200B4030E010.mp4?label=mp4_ld&amp;template=640x360.25.0&amp;ori=0&amp;ps=1CwnkDw1GXwCQx&amp;Expires=1710537294&amp;ssig=CS20HbBDfZ&amp;KID=unistore,video"><p>视频无法显示，请前往<a href="https://video.weibo.com/show?fid=1034%3A5011188891713616" target="_blank" rel="noopener noreferrer">微博视频</a>观看。</p></video>]]></description>
